               "expr": "sum(\n  rate(\n    envoy_http_downstream_rq_xx{\n      cluster=\"$cluster\",\nnamespace=~\"$namespace\",\njob=~\"$job\",\npod=~\"$pod\"\n\n\n    }[1h]\n  )\n) by (envoy_response_code_class)\n",
